<section class="about-section fade-in">
    <h1>About Neema Gospel Church</h1>
    <p class="intro">Neema Gospel Church is a Christ-centered ministry committed to discipleship, worship, and transforming lives.</p>

    <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-card">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>We exist to help people experience the life-giving flow of God’s love and grace, and to equip them to live out their God-given purpose.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-card">
            <h2>Our Vision</h2>
            <p>To love God, disciple, be equipped and empowered for service.
</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-card">
            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <p>God First, Reaching Out, Accepting our Assignment, Creating Community, Empowering Others.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

